import React, { useState } from "react"; import { warranties } from "../data/warranties"; import { Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableHead, TableRow, Paper, FormControl, InputLabel, Select, MenuItem, } from "@mui/material"; export default function WarrantyTable() { const [filter, setFilter] = useState("All"); const filtered = filter === "All" ? warranties : warranties.filter(w => w.status === filter); return (
Status Filter Customer Name Product Name Purchase Date Serial Number Status {filtered.map((w, i) => ( {w.customerName} {w.productName} {w.purchaseDate} {w.serialNumber} {w.status} ))}
); }
